    "To address RQ1, RQ2, and RQ4, we evaluate the zero-shot ranking efficacy of LLMs by using prompts as illustrated in Fig. 2(a).",
    "In the context of RQ3, we fine-tune LLaMA-based LLMs to act as CTR predictors, with the corresponding data sample presented in Fig. 2(b).",
